NK084(yu)002:1: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba 'di la gsum ste /
NK084(yu)002:8: dang po mngon du bya ba'i las dang /
NK084(yu)002:9: bar du ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:11: dang po sngon du bya ba'i las la drug ste /
NK084(yu)002:12: sbyin thos bsam pa'i snod dang /
NK084(yu)002:13: snod ngan pa la slob dpon byin pa'i skyon dang /
NK084(yu)002:14: mnyam pa'i mnyam la dam tshig bsrung ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:15: dngos grub dus bzhi sems yin pas logs na myed pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:16: mnyam bzhag gang gis bsgom pa las 'bras bu 'byung ba dpe' bstan pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:17: bsgom pa'i dgon pa gnas bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)002:18: bar du ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa la drug ste /
NK084(yu)002:19: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:20: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs ba la sogs pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:22: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)002:23: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:24: ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:26: bsgom pa la sogs la pa'i che ba'o //
NK084(yu)002:27: sems bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:28: dam bca' bdag dang ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:29: sems e ma'o ye shes lngar bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)002:31: ting nge sgrub pa'i 'dzin gyi dgongs pa dpes stan pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:32: de bzhin dngos rnams nyid dang /
NK084(yu)002:33: kun tu de bzhin snang dang /
NK084(yu)002:36: dam gzhi' rtsa bca' ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:37: yi ge a rab tu a la sems sbyang ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:38: ming tshogs de las ming gzhan la sems sbyang pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:39: ming tshogs gzhan la sems la sbyang ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:40: sems sbyangs 'di ni ba'i yon tan no //
NK084(yu)002:41: dkyil 'khor dngos bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:44: rten gzhal yas khang la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:45: 'byung ba de las dbang chen dang /
NK084(yu)002:49: cig char ye shes phyogs ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK084(yu)002:52: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo gyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK084(yu)002:55: rten pa lha la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:56: bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:57: rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i
NK084(yu)002:58: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya ba'o
NK084(yu)002:60: gtso bo a nibskyed pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:61: bdag sras bdag nyid sangs rgyas kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK084(yu)002:62: gsang thabs dang ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:63: sngags de la rkyen kyis phyir gdon pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:64: de dag rgyu rkyen sgyu 'phrul 'tshogs pa las 'byung bar bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)002:65: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya ba gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:69: skul bar de nas dam bca' ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:71: rtog pa sbyangs thabs dang pa'i dang /
NK084(yu)002:72: lha lha rnams kun 'od du zhu ba'o //
NK084(yu)002:73: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)002:77: nus pa ma h+aa dang ldan par bya'o //
NK084(yu)002:78: gtso' bo bskyed pa la bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)002:79: yab yum bskyed de nas snying po dran pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:80: dbang dang 'bru gsum byin brlabs bya ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:81: seng phrug yod mkha' h'u las 'das byin gyis brlabs te brdas bskul ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:82: byang sems sarba spros te chags mchod bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)002:84: yum gyi mkhar yum gyi pad ma byang chub sems las lhar bskyed pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:85: sngags kyis so so'i sngags phyir gdon pa'o //
NK084(yu)002:89: phyag mtshan rdo rje 'khor lo dang /
NK084(yu)002:91: zhi ba'i gnyen lcug tshul dgu' dang /
NK084(yu)002:93: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs ba la sogs pa la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:96: spyan drangs ba la drug ste /
NK084(yu)002:97: dam phyag rgya'i bca' ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:98: tshig gis spyan drangs ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:99: +amo e ha sngags kyis spyan drangs ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:100: rig pa'i me tog me tog dor la dor ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:101: dngos grub bskul ba badz+ra dang /
NK084(yu)002:102: gnyis dza h'u myed du bstim pa'o //
NK084(yu)002:104: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:105: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK084(yu)002:106: sta na thog mar sgrol ba'i 'ga' na gsal ldan sbyor ba'i dang /
NK084(yu)002:111: seng phrug phyag rgya la gsum ste /
NK084(yu)002:112: cig char seng phrug bar phyi'i phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)002:113: snyoms 'jug +amo dang mum gsang ba'i phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)002:114: rims kyis pa nang gi phyag rgya'o //
NK084(yu)002:115: cig char ba la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:116: sems sgyu 'phrul kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)002:118: phyag rgya spyi'i nges gsang ba de nyid tshig zhar byung ngo //
NK084(yu)002:119: rims kyis pa la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:120: phyag rgya 'byung mi bskyod ba'i rgyu dang /
NK084(yu)002:121: lha so so'i phyag 'bru bzhi' rgya bca' thabs so //
NK084(yu)002:122: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)002:123: lhag pa'i mchod pa'i ting nge 'dzin dngos dang /
NK084(yu)002:126: sku la +amo phyogs bstod pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:131: spyir +amo dang bsdus te bstod pa'o //
NK084(yu)002:133: dkyil 'khor bsnyen pa bsdu' ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:134: rgyun stong pa'i gyi spyod 'gro nyal lam dang /
NK084(yu)002:135: rtsa 'khor dkyil 'khor lo'i rdzogs rims so //
NK084(yu)002:136: tha mar tshogs bsgrub pa'i la bdun te /
NK084(yu)002:137: mtshan seng phrug nyid gsum gyis gzhi' shes 'jug gzung ba dang /
NK084(yu)002:138: yo byad dang du blangs sgyu 'phrul dra ba shing spyod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK084(yu)002:139: tshogs cho ga sngags dang bsgrubs pas tshe dbang thob pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:140: des de tshe bcu drug phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob dus dang /
NK084(yu)002:141: des lhun grub thob pa'i phyogs bcu dus bzhi pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK084(yu)002:142: des 'bras bu gcig dang du mar chos sku thob pa dang /
NK084(yu)002:143: yon tan de gzhan nas ma phyogs bcu dus bzhi byung bar bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)002:144: zhi ba'i bsdus don 'byed 'grel rdzogs soha //
